  m_text: "Hello, and welcome to my game!  In the spirit of My selected goal SDG
    15:  Life on land, we will be picking up some waste together! Walk up to the
    half eated sandwich, and pick it up with [E].       \nThe BIN (highlighted green)
    can be used to deposit rubbish (highlighted red) when you have items in your
    inventory!\nPick up all the rubbish on the map to win!\nGOOD LUCK"
